OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780398175
OL,3,CM6 shut in both directions as
OL,4,Cinvestigation Lorry crashes and
OL,5,Coverturns
OL,7,FA section of the M6 remains closed for
OL,8,Fpolice investigations after a lorry
OL,9,Fcrashed into the central reservation
OL,10,Fbarrier and overturned.
OL,12,FThe lorry hit the barrier shortly
OL,13,Fbefore 5 o'clock in the afternoon on
OL,14,FSunday. Emergency services attended
OL,15,Fthe scene, including the Air Ambulance.
OL,17,FThe motorway is closed on the
OL,18,FWarwickshire-Leicestershire border
OL,19,Fbetween junction one near Rugby and
OL,20,Fthe Catthorpe interchange.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
