OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780398175
OL,3,CM6 shut in both directions as
OL,4,Cinvestigation Lorry crashes and
OL,5,Coverturns
OL,7,FNational Highways says a police
OL,8,Finvestigation and recovery work are
OL,9,Fstill ongoing, and that there is no
OL,10,Festimated time for reopening.
OL,12,FThere are multiple diversion routes in
OL,13,Fplace, and drivers are being advised
OL,14,Fto check the national highways website.
OL,16,FAfter investigations, there is still
OL,17,Frecovery work, cleanup, and emergency
OL,18,Fwork to be done on the road surface
OL,19,Fand the damaged central reservation
OL,20,Fbarrier.
